# Xcode / Swift .gitignore
# Based on github/gitignore Swift + Xcode templates

## User settings & state
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

## Build artifacts
build/
DerivedData/
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM

## Generated project (XcodeGen produces this from project.yml)
*.xcodeproj

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/

## CocoaPods / Carthage (unused, but ignore if added later)
Pods/
Carthage/Build/

## Editor / tooling local state
.claude/

## macOS
.DS_Store

## Misc
*.swp
